                    <h2 class="name1">Martin Luther</h2>
                </div>
             
                <p class="content1">Our head artist and a humble guy. Born in goa, Martin has been a tattoo enthusiast since his childhood. He got his first tattoo at the early age of 14 on his wrist of his dog Leo who passed away that very summer. He went on learning more about tattoos since then which ended him up in one of the world’s best tattoo schools, the London Tattoo and Piercing Academy.</p>
                <p class="content1">For Martin, tattoo isn’t just a hobby, it’s his way of life, his way of expressing his thoughts. As for his specialization, Martin is a traditional guy. He specializes in Classic Americana, the fine blend of bold outline, similar colors and imagery&Portraiture- the realistic rendering of imageries, a genre he learned for Leo.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="Sana-Williams">
            <div class="box box2">
                <div class="img-heading-name2">
                    <img src="images/artists/Sana Williams.png" alt="" id="user2">
                    <h2 class="name2">Sana Williams</h2>
                </div>

            <p class="content2">Our unconventional lad, Sana was born in Kerala. Brought up in a conservative Catholic family, tattoo artist was definitely not among one of her parents’ carrier options for her, nor was Sana a tattoo enthusiast. It was when she met her boyfriend  at 17 (now her husband), her interest in tattoo kindled because she cherishes tattoo till this day and he encouraged her to get one. To express her love Sana got his name tattooed on his chest and since then she has dedicated her life to it. 
               <p class="content2"> She got her degree from the renowned Aliens Tattoo School. She specializes in Blackwork, the tribal gift to the modern world & Surrealism, the art of expressing the feeling of sublime fantasy. Surrealism is Sana’s favorite, because she gets to work with loads of material. You must try it.
               </p>
            </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="Zahid-Khan" name="Zahid-Khan">
