                    <h2 class="name3">Zahid Khan</h2>
                </div>
            <p class="content3">Our newbie and a tattoo freak, Zahid is an amazing artist. He found his interest in tattoos through the euphonious singer Justin Bieber. Zahid was born and brought up in Mumbai itself. Zahid is an intelligent guy and a good singer as well, but he is best at tattoo.
                <p class="content3">Zahid learned tattooing at Ace Tattooz & Art Studio. His specialization is Japanese which is an outcome of his love for anime, and he also specializes in New School, the crazy comic book on a body.
                </p> 
